Specifications:
["Sparx has officially launched the Neo 7 series with a brand new Ultra variant.
The Ultra variant packs some of the most powerful features available onthe market today, including an octa-core processor, 6GB of RAM, 128GB ofstorage, and a 6.6-inch display.
It also features a dual-camera setup and a 5,000 mAh battery withfast-charging capabilities.
It was just a few days ago that Sparx held a launching event in whichthey introduced the all-new Sparx's Neo 7 Ultra handset, which is a budgethandset with all the ultra features that we are going to reveal today.
There is no doubt that the massive 6.7-inch IPS LCD capacitivetouchscreen display of this device makes it very attractive.
The Neo 7 Ultra looks more premium with the small punch hole cutout on the top midsection of the display.
In addition to this, the display is capable of delivering a high resolution of 720 pixels by 1612 pixels.
The newly launched Sparx Neo 7's 6GB of RAM and 128GB of internal memory, with a dedicated memory card slot to expand the memory up to 256GB in the future.
The Sparx Neo's 7 Ultra features a very impressive camera design becauseof its large, round-shaped modules. Users will find a 50 MP + 2 MP sensor on the back of thephone, and the front of the phone will feature a 13 MP selfie sensor.
There is a huge 5000 mAh battery cell inside the Sparx Neo 7 Ultra,which is about to last for the entire day on just a single charge."]

Specifications:
["Sparx has officially launched the Neo 7 series with a brand new Ultra variant.
The Ultra variant packs some of the most powerful features available onthe market today, including an octa-core processor, 6GB of RAM, 128GB ofstorage, and a 6.6-inch display.
It also features a dual-camera setup and a 5,000 mAh battery withfast-charging capabilities.
It was just a few days ago that Sparx held a launching event in whichthey introduced the all-new Sparx's Neo 7 Ultra handset, which is a budgethandset with all the ultra features that we are going to reveal today.
There is no doubt that the massive 6.7-inch IPS LCD capacitivetouchscreen display of this device makes it very attractive.
The Neo 7 Ultra looks more premium with the small punch hole cutout on the top midsection of the display.
In addition to this, the display is capable of delivering a high resolution of 720 pixels by 1612 pixels.
The newly launched Sparx Neo 7's 6GB of RAM and 128GB of internal memory, with a dedicated memory card slot to expand the memory up to 256GB in the future.
The Sparx Neo's 7 Ultra features a very impressive camera design becauseof its large, round-shaped modules. Users will find a 50 MP + 2 MP sensor on the back of thephone, and the front of the phone will feature a 13 MP selfie sensor.
There is a huge 5000 mAh battery cell inside the Sparx Neo 7 Ultra,which is about to last for the entire day on just a single charge."]

Name: SPARX S3 2GB RAM 16GB ROM || 5.5" DISPLAY || 2700 mAh BATTERY || DUAL CAMERA || ONE YEAR BRAND WARRANTY || PTA APPROVED
Specifications:
["Smartphone brand Sparx has launched S3 smartphones in local markets recently.
This is a budget smartphone that offers a package of all the latest features that you could possibly want.
Sparx has made the S3 affordable for everyone by utilizing the latest hardware and software technologies.
This has allowed them to make a quality handset at a budget-friendly price, allowing customers to get the most out of their money.
First and foremost, the massive 5.45 Inches IPS LCD Capacitive Touchscreen display of the Sparx's S3 gives it a very premium look from an aesthetic perspective.
In fact, it's an HD display that is capable of displaying 720x1600 pixels very clearly.
After that, this brand new Sparx S3's Dual Cameras with 5 MP and 0.3 MP as well as a brighter LED flash for better light quality.
It will be equipped with a single 2MP selfie camera on the front that will be able to take beautiful portraits.
Aside from that, this S3 is powered by the well-known Unisoc SC9832E chipset with the addition of a 1.4Ghz Quad Core CPU for smooth and error-free operation without any lags or lag errors.
A big 2700mAh battery is featured on this S3 phone which ensures that it will easily last the whole day when recharged once. Also, there are no confirmed details about the Sparx S3 that will be released in the near future.
We will be updating you as soon as we have more information."]

Name: Google Pixel 4a 5G 6GB Ram 128GB Rom
Specifications:
['Introducing the Google Pixel 4a 5G – Your gateway to the future of mobile technology. This sleek and sophisticated smartphone combines the best of Google's innovation in a budget-friendly package.
**Stunning Display:** The Pixel 4a 5G features a vibrant 6.2-inch OLED display, providing sharp and vivid visuals for all your content. Whether you're streaming movies or scrolling through your social media feed, you'll be captivated by the stunning picture quality.
**5G Connectivity:** Experience the next level of connectivity with 5G support. Stream, download, and game faster than ever before, all while enjoying seamless video calls and lightning-fast data speeds.
**Impressive Camera:** Capture memories in exceptional detail with the Pixel 4a 5G's remarkable camera system. The 12.2MP main camera and 16MP ultra-wide lens ensure stunning photos in various lighting conditions. Google's renowned Night Sight technology allows you to take incredible low-light shots.
**All-Day Battery:** Stay powered up throughout the day with the Pixel 4a 5G's long-lasting battery. Whether you're working, playing, or streaming, this smartphone will keep up with your demands.
**Pure Android Experience:** Enjoy the latest Android updates and features as soon as they're released, thanks to Google's pure Android experience. Say goodbye to bloatware and enjoy a clean, user-friendly interface.
**Google Assistant:** With the Pixel 4a 5G, you have a personal Google Assistant at your fingertips. Just say "Hey Google" to get answers, manage your tasks, and control smart devices effortlessly.
**Security:** Rest easy knowing your data is secure with the Titan M security chip and frequent security updates.
The Google Pixel 4a 5G is the ideal choice for those who crave exceptional performance, photography, and connectivity without breaking the bank. It's the smartphone designed to keep you connected to what matters most in your life. Elevate your mobile experience with the Pixel 4a 5G today!
(Important note: This device has a high processor and high resolution display so heating up is common. No refund will issue if the mobile seal (sticker) is removed)']
